9.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:02:02.000Z","msg":"睇得出 MTR 同 CX 公會應該唔會嚮應"},{"pid":"58968f3ef8fd4b043241f420781e9fbc05ca8c43","tid":1381642,"uid":44174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:02:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d42d9b40958189652ba0f833dad199ef3dc626b2","tid":1381642,"uid":124452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9105d74fc36e6808717690408894ec7307fdfe8d","tid":1381642,"uid":207634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:04:12.000Z","msg":"冇錯，香港前途靠你地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ead7a6a2be29c9cb2d659c70c887a7a1508865","tid":1381642,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:04:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">海陸空<br />\n全民同一陣線</span></span>"},{"pid":"84de77dc246ef1d5352068620236d4a27c82e7ef","tid":1381642,"uid":207634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:04:40.000Z","msg":"推到有真普選"},{"pid":"c1db28b37cfd0d919289c10a56b1ab6185ebc6cc","tid":1381642,"uid":153938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:18:12.000Z","msg":"612已經有唔少國泰crew罷工，令到公司要打電話迫啲放𡁵假嘅返工。今次最好呼籲埋調配人手嘅crew control 罷工啦，冇機起飛到都似。"},{"pid":"e2919643d91b08c0b7095af6b2f34eb2c6c76655","tid":1381642,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:18:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"b7f5177e894bd45e927563b64ffee1e6dd5fd586","tid":1381642,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:19:01.000Z","msg":"支持香港人"},{"pid":"a28af9d482656d8d373f08edb6835011079a70ec","tid":1381642,"uid":190637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:19:32.000Z","msg":"仲有公務員呀"},{"pid":"e7d3e1e7069f069260454a16444a863a1150558c","tid":1381642,"uid":223353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1db28b37cfd0d919289c10a56b1ab6185ebc6cc","tid":1381642,"uid":153938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:18:12.000Z","msg":"612已經有唔少國泰crew罷工，令到公司要打電話迫啲放𡁵假嘅返工。今次最好呼籲埋調配人手嘅crew control 罷工啦，冇機起飛到都似。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:04:36.000Z","msg":"要成事太困難<br />\n就咁睇佢地公海既取態都...."},{"pid":"db0e270695176eaad5ce6a87a9c41462583a422c","tid":1381642,"uid":223353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a28af9d482656d8d373f08edb6835011079a70ec","tid":1381642,"uid":190637,"like":0,"d